rComments: Taught a class about muppets. Looked like a muppet. Loved to talk about muppets. Boring class though. Waste of time. Make sure to take it with a friend or you will die.

She promotes films without content. Loves to rattle on about cultural history and hates it if you disagree with her or her films. She will hold a grudge & is very batty, easily amused & distracted. Doesn't explain class expectations well. The class is very easy, except for the week of the festival (8 films, 5 days, 3 locations, 0 content).
